@MartinSusky an hour on "Loading..." is definitely a bug, not the normal first-run delay. To dig in, please attach the helper logs so we can see where the ACP session stalls:

`%LOCALAPPDATA%\Packages\<IntelligentTerminal PFN>\LocalCache\Local\IntelligentTerminal\logs\` - specifically `wta-main_master.log` and `wta-main_helper-*.log`.

Also: is `claude` on your PATH and does `claude` run from a normal terminal? If the agent CLI can't launch, the master never connects and the pane stays on Loading. See https://github.com/microsoft/intelligent-terminal#collecting-logs
